  m_RaycastTarget: 1
  m_RaycastPadding: {x: 0, y: 0, z: 0, w: 0}
  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Alnebaal is a desert, with lots of beautiful oasises and vegetation near
    the borders of Draichtbaile and Dundria. While mostly the architecture is of
    sandstone, their fabrics decorate the city in a beautiful and colorful delight.
    \n\nThe nation\u2019s speciality is nothing other than fashion. As Alnebaal is
    home to the most exquisite textures and fabrics, their fashion is nothing short
    of the standard in the nation.\n\nAlnebaal is the only nation with several rulers,
    but the lord himself is none other than Lord Kamuzu, also known as Al-Kamuzu.
    Al-Kamuzu is fixated on repairing the consequences of past rulers and even to
    this day repairs the damages of what the first lord did to the entirety of Grankalia.
    The journey still has a long way to go, and he knows some of his people still
    have the opressive mindset, but he is certain the nation can be forgiven and
    can move on as a nation celebrating differences. "
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
