  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Garasu Kingdom, while being the majority of the year in some layers of
    snow, is a land perfect for athletes in winter sports. Other areas of the countries
    are tundra, mountains and frozen oceans. \n\nIf you want to experience festivals
    and parties, Garasu Kingdom is the land to go to. With several small ones and
    major festivals taking place during the months, you\u2019d never be bored. Each
    festival is to honor something, like a piece of history or even something as
    small as a day dedicated to pancakes. \n\nThe land is set to be ruled by the
    lord Kensuke Tachikawa, also known as Crown Prince Kensuke. While he does certainly
    rule it at the moment his mother is ill, he has yet to be coronated. Unfortunately
    Garasu Kingdom has the highest crime rate in all of Grankalia, but the prince
    plans to take action against it, whatever it takes. "
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 5302535af1044152a457ed104f1f4b91, type: 2}
