  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "The only nation with both land and sea civilization. At land you can find
    beautiful tropical resorts and some of the best beaches in Grankalia. In the
    deeper seas you can find beautiful corals and cities. If you dare eat seagrass,
    you can even experience the wonders of the sea. \n\nThis nation has got you covered
    for various tournaments and leisure sporting. One of their trademark sports is
    splashball, one of the only sports played fully under water. \n\nThis nation
    is ruled by Lord Elena, the Queen of the sea. She resides mostly in her palace,
    but her daughter, Princess Centaine finds time both at land and sea. Queen Elena
    makes sure her seas are trash free and will hunt down litterers and thieves for
    sport. This makes the lands of The Pelagic Archipelago neglected and taken care
    of by trusted harpies. While tourism is strong, the locals believe they should
    make their living less reliant on tourists. "
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 5302535af1044152a457ed104f1f4b91, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 2164040, guid: 5302535af1044152a457ed104f1f4b91, type: 2}
