  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Grankalia is a world directly connected to the human world, yet very few
    have had the chance to travel to this dimension. \n\nGrankalia is home to all
    sorts of creatures, both humanoid and not. In Dundria you find humans, Garasu
    Kingdom crystal shifters, Sorus elementals, Draichtbaile mushroomers, The Pegalic
    Archipelago oceanids and in Alnebaal djinns. Although these are unique to each
    nation, a species they all have in common are animal/human hybrids. \n\nArtes
    are quite uncommon in Grankalia, with most sorcerers residing in Dundria. That
    does not make artes uncommon to witness by the ordinary folk, since sorcerers
    are well paid for social gatherings and festivals to enhance the experience for
    everybody. "
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 5302535af1044152a457ed104f1f4b91, type: 2}
