  m_text: "A posh, yet caring man with an expertise in teleportation artes. Vincent
    is a man of elegance, but doesn\u2019t suck up to the higher class. \n\nHe particularly
    enjoys books and is seen most of the time sticking his nose into one of his favorite
    authors' latest volumes."
