  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Sorus is a warm and colorful nation best known for it\u2019s music culture. 
    Steep mountains, saharas, canyons and beautiful waterfalls are some of the cultural
    landmarks of this nation and perfect for any music fan and hiker. \n\nFestivals
    are common in many parts of Sorus, but the festivals there are of a whole different
    vibe. Most carnivals are for dancing and celebrating life as a whole. The highlight
    of this nation is the annual song contest held in Los Oros, where each nation
    sends an artist who competes for the trophy of the best song.\n\nLord Cadenza,
    also known as Abuela Cadenza in Sorus, is on the older side, but respected by
    both the locals and her fellow lords. She is one of the only lords who attend
    almost every event happening in the nation. But due to her older age, she has
    a bit of a harder time cleaning up the nation of it\u2019s many gangs and criminal
    organizations. \n"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 5302535af1044152a457ed104f1f4b91, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 2164040, guid: 5302535af1044152a457ed104f1f4b91, type: 2}
